                      boolean friend,
                      User confirmer)
        Checks a User to see if that User is already in another User's friends list. If they are, they are removed from the friends list, if they are not, add that User to the list.
        Parameters:
        requester - User who requests the friendship
        friend - boolean that returns True if User is already a friend.
        confirmer - User who receives the request for friendship.
